info.author: Anil Kumar
info.description:
A multi-platform multi-lanuage source code browsing tool.
A pyQt GUI front-end for idutils, cscope and gtags.
Written in python using pyQt, QScintilla libraries.

With idutils backend, supports all languages supported by ctags like C, C++, Java, Python etc
info.keywords: idutils, cscope, gtags, CodeAnalysis, CodeBrowsing, pyQt, qscintilla, python
info.name: seascope
